# Sub-Command

Name Type Description Default Required
name String (opens new window) The name of the sub-command None Yes
description String (opens new window) The description of the sub-command None Yes
type ApplicationCommandOptionType (opens new window) The type of the sub-command None No
required Boolean (opens new window) If the sub-command is required or not None No
choices ApplicationCommandOptionChoice (opens new window) If the sub-command is required or not None No
options CommandArg Additional options None No
